{"type":null,"faqId":38495,"title":"升级手机","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:1.3784722in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p6{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p7{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{color:blue;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p></p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125458\" style=\"width:0.93680555in;height:0.43680555in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">使用非授权第三方软件升级手机的固件和系统，可能存在手机无法使用或者泄漏您个人信息等安全风险。建议您使用在线升级或者下载与手机型号匹配的官方软件进行升级。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">手机升级后，您所有的个人信息可能会被移除，请在升级前备份个人信息。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">1.在线升级</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在进行在线升级手机之前，请确保手机已连接到网络。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125459\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">”“设置”。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在“全部设置”页签下，点击“系统更新”。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“检查更新”。若有新版本，可根据屏幕提示完成下载和安装。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125460\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在线升级需要耗费一定的流量，建议在WLAN环境下升级。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">2.</span><a name=\"_task_update_software_local-chtext\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">本地升级</span></a>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">XE \"本地升级\"在进行本地升级之前，请先进入 </span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/%22 \\o %22 \"><span class=\"s2\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> 下载软件升级包，并将软件升级包中的 dload 文件夹放入手机内部存储的根目录下。如果手机支持 microSD 卡，您还可以将其放入 microSD 卡的根目录下。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125461\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">”“设置”。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在“全部设置”页签下，点击“系统更新”。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125462\" style=\"width:0.25694445in;height:0.18333334in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> &gt; 本地升级”，根据屏幕提示完成升级。</span></span>\n</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">3.</span><a name=\"_task_update_software_USB-chtext\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">U 盘升级</span></a>\n</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">XE \"U 盘升级\"在进行 U 盘升级之前，请先进入 </span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/%22 \\o %22 \"><span class=\"s2\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> 下载软件升级包，并将软件升级包中的 dload 文件夹放入 U 盘的根目录下。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125463\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">请使用华为认可的 USB OTG 数据线，如需购买，请联系您的手机供应商。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">使用 USB OTG 数据线连接手机和 U 盘。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125464\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">”“设置”。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在“全部设置”页签下，点击“系统更新”。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125465\" style=\"width:0.25694445in;height:0.18333334in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> &gt; U 盘升级”，根据屏幕提示完成升级。</span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":141,"faqType":"备份恢复与升级","useful":2,"unUseful":6,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3775","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Backup-Restore-Update","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441448684000,"seriesProductName":"GRA-CL00,GRA-CL10,GRA-TL00,GRA-UL00,GRA-UL10","visitedTimes":628,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"升级手机","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}